","tid":1118561,"uid":20867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T14:46:03.000Z","msg":"#賣白粉"},{"pid":"76631470a1478366b8c04e09bcd6d281ca62fcbc","tid":1118561,"uid":202698,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T14:55:25.000Z","msg":"呢個post應該好快被連仔del<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c36233b38b7a9d7f0cae240d56d9b6f9d317c0c1","tid":1118561,"uid":117200,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T14:57:26.000Z","msg":"得罪Google應該仲撚大鍋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc8299682b210d8459f7d62a181093c6e6c1ff3a","tid":1118561,"uid":51066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T15:05:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/fea/scandal/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Ffea%2Fscandal%2F&d=CcUT5H46krin9iWjsTG5RGo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=a5ed8075\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/fea/scandal/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29ff5a3bde3580bb7b944ad0368d150963f91732","tid":1118561,"uid":7076,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T15:41:53.000Z","msg":"咁樣Google係咪應該係佢個search engine 到完全remove東方/related東方內容嘅link<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時睇吓邊個出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6915c1cf07db6087f4d7b541af9376dcae3ffdf6","tid":1118561,"uid":179409,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"5614c252d14efc81945282e763ec2f7f3fb45171","tid":1118561,"uid":90323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T14:07:41.000Z","msg":"誹謗乜野。。。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T19:07:34.000Z","msg":"呢個真心唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果同關鍵字有關<br />\n咁都係搜尋用戶多人搜尋部份字眼<br />\n先會咁顯示<br />\n其實Google確實無權<br />\n亦唔應該干預關鍵字會點出<br />\n而且Google都無能力判斷搜尋內容嘅真偽<br />\n有無熟法律嘅巴打解釋下？"},{"pid":"ba287b90d4eb1217cfa4668962cf3e971db218b0","tid":1118561,"uid":119607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T19:17:29.000Z","msg":"因為賣白粉？"},{"pid":"5e5f4f21bb0cb943181d97c322d815c756158241","tid":1118561,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba287b90d4eb1217cfa4668962cf3e971db218b0","tid":1118561,"uid":119607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T19:17:29.000Z","msg":"因為賣白粉？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T19:41:29.000Z","msg":"日賣白份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ebba53c47a738a61e4700e5289f573095ca3827","tid":1118561,"uid":20522,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T20:12:43.000Z","msg":"幫東方正視聽先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根據1978年9月20日《大公報》載，高等法院開審大販毒疑案前夕，馬惜珍突潛逃。<br />\n<br />\n律政司控告馬氏兄弟偷運之700噸鴉片，比「跛豪」吳錫豪被控偷運數量的30噸多23倍，根據律政司控告「跛豪」的罪名內容，30噸鴉片時值3億港元，以此推算，馬氏兄弟偷運之鴉片應值70億港元，以六七十年代及2010年代港幣購買力比較(保守估計為1比50)，相當於今日3500億港元。"},{"pid":"a86e74c35c2f70388da17e35755f1aac1b0628a6","tid":1118561,"uid":31389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T20:55:26.000Z","msg":"俾幾個碎銀你當破財擋災"},{"pid":"72fd5467e98833311173c941ad05c1509ec36bc9","tid":1118561,"uid":78143,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T21:16:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iFEUM6b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiFEUM6b.jpg&h=6fd5a9cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EtZBfZw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEtZBfZw.jpg&h=2f910e43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ecwW0rb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FecwW0rb.jpg&h=cbc68d7d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e87126de9f801a698fc1a7ee